{"tid":1816880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉到鬼又點？你敢打狗咩？","createTime":"2020-01-08T15:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T15:59:11.000Z","uid":38170,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"455a4dbdfe54290cf392e29104d682a528402edd","tid":1816880,"uid":38170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"捉鬼，捉錯手足就影響士氣<br />\n好喇 真係捉到狗，咁又點？<br />\n你敢打狗咩？<br />\n<br />\n唯一可以阻止狗扮手足<br />\n就係要打狗<br />\n<br />\n點解藍絲而家唔敢出黎挑機？<br />\n點解大陸人唔敢出黎挑機？<br />\n點解鄉黑唔敢出黎挑機？<br />\n因為我地搵到佢 之後獅鳥<br />\n獅到佢地驚<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n唯一可以阻止狗扮手足<br />\n就係要打狗"},{"pid":"75048e6ab8d50951a8d08e0470bd9cf45aee7ab7","tid":1816880,"uid":38170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"將軍澳咁 明明班鬼出手拉人<br />\n好喇 咁鐘意捉鬼<br />\n鬼現晒形 班捉鬼敢死隊又淨係尻叫放人<br />\n我係狗呀 梗係場場都落鬼啦<br />\n無人捉到可以分化<br />\n俾人捉到 拎枝棍仔出黎就甩到身<br />\n根本0成本"},{"pid":"7301f532bc436ee7caa31243f5341d58f6974fdf","tid":1816880,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"真，推"},{"pid":"af8fffcd78f9f0b6eb711390e44755d0abff29b4","tid":1816880,"uid":38170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"勇武真解散又好假又好<br />\n要解決鬼呢個問題唔係在於捉唔捉<br />\n係在於捉到之後<br />\n要所有人去打狗先得架嘛<br />\n捉完放佢走 捉黎把撚呀？<br />\n定係以為捉完有人會幫你出頭去打狗呀？<br />\n自己就可以獨善其身又拎捉鬼光環？<br />\n邊有咁便宜既事呀？<br />\n有心上得場<br />\n大家都係爭取緊同一樣野<br />\n點解想捉鬼又唔肯落手打？<br />\n咁先係幫勇武 咁先係和勇合一<br />\n咁先係光復香港呀屌你老味"},{"pid":"db7fe3d58b03c7a38f1d0123b8ffff219d6e93ab","tid":1816880,"uid":38170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解班狗唔再放煙呀？<br />\n因為放煙唔好睇又攪埋自己人呀<br />\n落鬼無成本 點解我唔繼續落？"},{"pid":"19c262bd753eeebb0eee8071e09c26056714d865","tid":1816880,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"「靠你地搞革命死得啦，企係度唔知做乜」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690786</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f8808add3167895c82d6797522f667dcc2dfeeb","tid":1816880,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d48c26b6894d54a14f51126a06ad6d4fffae4461","tid":1816880,"uid":38170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"周同學死左兩個月<br />\n報咩仇？"},{"pid":"e689afcc8c8e76c20afc454cabb65e4a8912359d","tid":1816880,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"開槍點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea6110596282c04abc392a0e3050eaae4749b9c","tid":1816880,"uid":38170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e689afcc8c8e76c20afc454cabb65e4a8912359d","tid":1816880,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"開槍點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"我點知點算呀<br />\n布袋彈射爆眼咁點算呀？唔出去呀？<br />\n催淚煙有毒咁又點算呀？屋企抗爭呀？"},{"pid":"c4ec9cab016c02b72ec4b1436cc70cab1286ef42","tid":1816880,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻豬仔可以驅鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8a8bcf9d31c3e7c140b15fb0d54bf6a22f94f1","tid":1816880,"uid":38170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"我哋唔係要捉鬼<br />\n係打鬼"},{"pid":"7199973a2c5cbf50f3a0f0c9296d237a6cfce55f","tid":1816880,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"好聲好氣問兩句<br />\n好過無禮貌咁捉"}]}